race.comment: KADALL (6) resumes here but the form he showed when last in work was good enough for a race of this nature. Saves his best form for this distance range and a strong showing while fresh would not surprise. VORACIOUS (8) has been thereabouts in Saturday grade of late and gets the deadly Gollan/Maloney combination. Has to be included. MORE TROUBLE (10) strips fitter second-up from the spell and can trouble the judge with luck in running. BEWS (2) strips fitter third-up, draws the inside gate and gets 3kg off. Ticks plenty boxes for a race of this nature. CUNNAMULLA FELLA (1) best of the rest with the claim.
